title: 294: Sneaky-good draft picks
itunes:title: 294: Sneaky-good draft picks
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks continue to recap the 2018 NFL Draft, but kick things off by discussing the retirement of tight end Jason Witten & if he’s a first ballot Hall of Famer (1:52). The guys then reveal sneaky-good draft picks for all 32 teams (5:41), followed by their favorite running back team fits (49:24).
